Make a pattern that will match three consecutive copies of whatever is cur‐ rently contained in $what. That is, if $what
is fred, your pattern should match fredfredfred. If $what is fred|barney, your pattern should match fredfredbarney or
barneyfredfred or barneybarneybarney or many other variations. (Hint: you should set $what at the top of the pattern
test program with a statement like my $what = 'fred|barney';.)
